[ NEW SPORTS CAR AVAILABLE: Prepare yourself for an uncompromising roadster that merges elegant design, high-end performance and trend-setting innovation. Add the Porsche Boxster S to your exclusive fleet of cars and find out what it is like to feel the airflow on your skin when you speed along the asphalt with more than 170mph. ]
Sports Car Challenge is a fast-paced racing experience for your Android phone with graphics and gameplay never seen before on a smartphone or tablet. Enjoy the sheer beauty and amazing details of the hottest high-end sportscars from Audi, Bentley, Bugatti, Lamborghini, Porsche and Volkswagen, while you speed along the track with up to 250 miles per hour.
