Shift through the seven gears of the Bugatti Veyron 16.4 Grand Sport and indulge in the stunning looks of the Bentley Continental GT V8 or Bentley Continental Convertible ISR. Set new track records with the Lamborghini Aventador LP 700-4 or Lamborghini Gallardo LP 570-4 Superleggera and manoeuvre the Audi R8 GT Spyder or Audi TTS CoupÃƒÂ© through the demanding slalom course. Master the challenging braking contest with the Porsche 911 Carrera S or the Porsche Cayman R and kick the pedal of the Volkswagen Scirocco R to the metal. Show your friends that you can beat their personal high scores at ease and dominate the global leaderboards!
- Time Trial
- Slalom
- Braking
With realistic driving physics, authentic engine sounds and manifold customization options on account of an exclusive selection of original rims and paintworks, Sports Car Challenge offers an unprecedented racing experience on Android devices. And due to a number of free content-updates, which will add more cars and tracks to the title in the upcoming months, the challenge wonÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t be over anytime soonÃ¢â‚¬Â¦ do you have what it takes to master the hottest sports cars in the word and reach the finish line of four demanding circuits in minimum time?
- Black Forest Germany
- Shanghai Audi International Circuit
- Singapore by Night
- Yunlong Lake China
- Zhuhai International Circuit
Sports Car Challenge has been created and developed by FISHLABS Entertainment and is powered by the ABYSS game engine.
